{"tid":708966,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個討論區越出名，就會越低質","createTime":"2018-06-19T15:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T15:51:40.000Z","uid":150100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9ff74a107e8202a946836f9c591a9477f223c0","tid":708966,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"依個根本係金科玉律嚟<br />\n<br />\n一個討論區之所以會由唔出名到出名，一定係因為內容高質、有創意吸引到人，好似以前舊登、連登咁。我自己都係因為咁先down同開ac啫。但就係因為咁，就會有越嚟越多on9湧入，加上網上匿名講野唔使負責任，討論內容就會好似宜家連登咁，偏激而且冇人性，幼稚同愚蠢。唔係話成個連登都低質，但至少相比以前同埋舊登係差好多。<br />\n<br />\n其實真係唔單止連登係咁，台灣個ptt，大陸個知乎，都係因高質而出名，因出名而越趨低質。<br />\n<br />\n純粹有感而發，無意針對任何人或事。有時我寧願連登少啲人用，但係討論內容高質。"},{"pid":"9b9ace4a81e0e3ebae3ec8571bc16dace5db7341","tid":708966,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dd867c505f485e1e6308bceeb29f06800a6af9","tid":708966,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"Reddit 4chan?"},{"pid":"8dd48987fb6db64077249ba957cffb356b7251b2","tid":708966,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26dd867c505f485e1e6308bceeb29f06800a6af9","tid":708966,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"Reddit 4chan?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"reddit少上，上嚟都係為咗睇波<br />\n4chan直情冇上<br />\n所以冇提"},{"pid":"41811f97dbc19354a39c93a38f5a251f27cb94d7","tid":708966,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"或者外國嘅會好啲嘅，中港台喺低質方面真係一家親，旗鼓相當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7911527281a343d2629c055a2c44e29f5c552f93","tid":708966,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5338dd0794c9c5d51dbbc20c554